// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1695 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1f942395-de4e-540f-bd97-0cdbf813e7e0

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
